                     <interp inst="t18440408-1190-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 1 bag, value 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 16 half-crowns, 20 shillings, and 40 sixpences; the property of <persName id="t18440408-name-907" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-907" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
